  "Georg Nemetschek is the founder and deputy chairman of software company Nemetschek Group, which employs over 2,800 workers in 82 locations.",
  "He started using design software in his own engineering office in the late 1960s, long before computers became available for personal use.",
  "The company, which serves the architecture, engineering and construction industries, went public in 1999.",
  "Nemetschek Group expanded into 3D animation and motion design, securing access to the media industry. Its software has around 5 million users.",
  "Georg still owns a majority stake directly and through his family asset management firm."
